<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="declare-v">declare <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'kleə(r)/    美 /dɪ'kler/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>宣布；声明</strong></h4>
<p>to say sth officially or publicly：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In September 1939, Britain <strong>declared war on</strong> Germany after Germany invaded Poland.  
1939年9月，在德国入侵波兰后，英国向德国宣战。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 6</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>declare + that 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The court declared that strike action was illegal. 
法院宣布那次罢工行为是违法的。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>declare sth / sb (to be) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The area has been declared a national park. 
已宣布这个地区成为国家公园。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>declare sth + adj:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The chairman declared the ceremony open; all of us at present cheered. 
主席宣布仪式开始，我们在场的所有人都欢呼雀跃。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>声称；宣称</strong></h4>
<p>to state sth firmly and clearly：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He declared that he would put humans on Mars in less than a decade.
他宣称，在十年内要将人类送上火星。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Ella <strong>declared herself</strong> (<strong>to be</strong>) happy and satisfied. 
埃拉声称自己非常幸福和满足。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>申报 (纳税品等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you have nothing to declare, go through the Green Channel.  
如果你没有东西要申报，那就走绿色通道。</p></div></div>